== 制作 ==
2008年5月，在[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]上，[[米高梅|米高梅]]的哈利·斯隆（{{lang|en|Harry Sloan}}）和玛丽·佩伦特（{{lang|en|Mary Parent}}）宣布《赤色黎明》[[重制|重制]]版进入[[前期制作|前期制作]]初期阶段，重拍将由此前在《[[谍影重重|谍影重重]]》、《[[蜘蛛侠3|蜘蛛侠3]]》、《[[独立日_(电影)|独立日]]》和《[[大破量子危机|大破量子危机]]》等片中担任{{le|第二单元|Second unit|第二单元导演}}和[[动作指导|动作指导]]的{{le|丹·布拉德利|Dan Bradley}}导演。米高梅后来宣布电影将被重制得“牢记我们所处的后[[九一一|九一一]]时代<ref name="thr45">{{cite news |title='Red Dawn' redo lands director, scribe; MGM will remake the 1984 action drama |first=Jay A. |last=Fernandez |author2=Borys Kit |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i28e0d4f7991010721fa8d721c07ce0eb?imw=Y |date=2008-07-09 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2016-07-02 |archive-date=2010-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100520014755/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i28e0d4f7991010721fa8d721c07ce0eb?imw=Y |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |work=The Hollywood Reporter |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3idda2f1661c03a55f6d1b4663fa9ec2ae |title=MGM: Two up for a remake treatment — MGM may remake the '80s action films |first=Steven |last=Zeitchik |date=2008-05-17 |accessdate=2016-07-02 |archive-date=2008-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080605142725/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3idda2f1661c03a55f6d1b4663fa9ec2ae |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”当月的晚些时候，米高梅宣布丹·布拉德利已被确认为导演，《[[红眼航班|红眼航班]]》和《[[后窗惊魂|后窗惊魂]]》编剧{{le|卡尔·埃尔斯沃斯|Carl Ellsworth}}负责创作改编剧本<ref name="thr45"/><ref>{{cite web |last=Bartyzel |first=Monika |url=http://www.cinematical.com/2008/07/09/red-dawn-remake-finds-writer-and-director/ |title='Red Dawn' Remake Finds Writer and Director |publisher=Cinematical |date=2008-07-09 |accessdate=2009-06-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120722025215/http://blog.moviefone.com/2008/07/09/red-dawn-remake-finds-writer-and-director/ |archivedate=2012-07-22 }}</ref>。埃尔斯沃斯将与杰里米·帕斯默共同编剧。{{le|文森特·纽曼|Vincent Newman}}（《[[单刀直入|单刀直入]]》）宣布担任制作人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=46707 |title=Ellsworth Penning Red Dawn Remake |publisher=ComingSoon.net |accessdate=2009-06-17 |archive-date=2014-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113093745/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=46707 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。澳大利亚演员[[克里斯·海姆斯沃斯|克里斯·海姆斯沃斯]]被选为主角<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadlinehollywooddaily.com/exclusive-chris-hemsworth-is-thor/ |title=Nikki Finke’s Deadline Hollywood Daily » EXCLUSIVE: Chris Hemsworth Is 'Thor' |publisher=Deadlinehollywooddaily.com |accessdate=2009-06-17 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5yabdpEZ5?url=http://www.deadline.com/2009/05/exclusive-chris-hemsworth-is-thor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他演员阵容包括[[乔希·佩克|乔希·佩克]]、[[乔什·哈切森|乔什·哈切森]]、[[阿德琳妮·帕里奇|阿德琳妮·帕里奇]]、[[伊莎贝尔·卢卡斯|伊莎贝尔·卢卡斯]]、[[康纳·克鲁斯|康纳·克鲁斯]]和[[杰弗里·迪恩·摩根|杰弗里·迪恩·摩根]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Fernandez |first=Jay A. |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ic709b2a7b82e176c839b6dd393db75df |title=Two cast in 'Red Dawn' remake |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |accessdate=2009-06-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620072543/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ic709b2a7b82e176c839b6dd393db75df |archivedate=2009-06-20 }}</ref>。

影片于2009年9月在[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[芒特克莱门斯|芒特克莱门斯]]开拍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/42366|title=Pics From The Set Of The RED DAWN Remake!!|publisher=Ain't It Cool News|date=2009-09-15|accessdate=2009-09-15|archive-date=2018-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181222093526/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/42366|dead-url=no}}</ref>。密歇根州（{{tsl|en|Metro Detroit|底特律都會區|大底特律都市区}}）的{{le|哈珀伍兹市|Harper Woods}}{{le|诺特丹高中|Notre Dame High School}}被关闭用作取景地<ref>Binelli, p. 260.</ref>。《待在底特律城》（{{lang|en|''Detroit City Is the Place to Be''}}）的作者马克·比内利（{{lang|en|Mark Binelli}}）写道，学校食堂被用作剧组成员饭堂<ref>Binelli, p. 260-261.</ref>。根据拍摄于该地的剧照，电影出现的宣传小册子、海报和横幅带有[[中国人民解放军|中国人民解放军]]的軍徽或旗幟。海报意在争取对中国侵略的支持，标语诸如“重建你们的声誉”、“恢复你们的经济”和“打击企业腐败”之类<ref name=tiexue>{{cite web|url=http://bbs.tiexue.net/post_3860219_1.html|title=好莱坞翻拍冷战时大片 "中国军人"穿07迷彩"入侵美国"|publisher=铁血网|accessdate=2009-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091003121227/http://bbs.tiexue.net/post_3860219_1.html|archive-date=2009-10-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="ifeng">{{cite news|url=http://news.ifeng.com/mil/3/200909/0930_341_1371284.shtml|title=好莱坞翻拍冷战时大片 剧情变为中国“入侵美国”|date=2009-09-30|publisher=凤凰网|accessdate=2009-10-10|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210233749/http://news.ifeng.com/mil/3/200909/0930_341_1371284.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年6月，影片发行由于[[米高梅|米高梅陷入财务危机]]而被搁置。搁置之际{{le|锥子网|The Awl}}泄露的剧本摘录在中国引发越来越大的争议。影片引发中国官方媒体之一《[[环球时报|环球时报]]》的尖锐批评。该报撰写题为《美国重拍冷战片妖魔化中国》和《美国电影播种针对中国的敌对种子》的文章。其中一篇文章指出：“中国依然能感受到美国的不信任和恐惧，特别是其人民之间。美国对中国的怀疑是鹰派传播恐惧和怀疑的最佳理由，这是这部电影《赤色黎明》最大的关注点<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/2010/06/10/more-mgm-fallout-red-dawn-delayed-perhaps-indefinitely/|title=More MGM Fallout: Red Dawn Delayed, Perhaps Indefinitely?|author=Russ Fischer|publisher=''/Film''|date=2010-06-10|accessdate=2010-06-15|archive-date=2012-09-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120918022853/http://www.slashfilm.com/2010/06/10/more-mgm-fallout-red-dawn-delayed-perhaps-indefinitely/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i9a9ec43069ab4f97784bd1acb15d858d|title=Chinese press rails against 'Red Dawn'|author=Jonathan Landreth|publisher=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2010-06-01|accessdate=2010-06-15|archive-date=2012-12-08|archive-url=https://archive.today/20121208172311/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i9a9ec43069ab4f97784bd1acb15d858d|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

2011年1月，第一批剧照发布，伴随而来的是一旦米高梅的[[美国法典第十一章第十一条|第十一条]]重组完成，影片将发行的消息。影片是米高梅三部预计于2011年发行的已完成作品中的其中一部<ref name="dailyblam">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailyblam.com/news/2011/01/03/new-cast-photo-release-info-for-red-dawn-remake-starring-chris-hemsworth-jeffrey-dea|title=New Cast Photo & Release Info for RED DAWN Starring Chris Hemsworth & Jeffrey Dean Morgan|author=Pietro Filipponi|work=The Daily Blam!|date=2011-01-03|accessdate=2011-01-04|archive-date=2020-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112023448/http://www.dailyblam.com/news/2011/01/03/new-cast-photo-release-info-for-red-dawn-remake-starring-chris-hemsworth-jeffrey-dea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年3月，《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》报道称，米高梅已将电影中的反派从中国改成朝鲜，确保影片能获得中国利润丰厚的票房。据称改动成本不超过100万美元，涉及概括剧情虚构背景的开头片段（放弃了中国在美国[[主权违约|违约]]侵略朝鲜后{{le|收回资产|repossession}}的原本剧情）、重新剪辑了两个镜头、利用数字技术将中国标志和对白改成朝鲜的<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.vulture.com/2011/12/red-dawn-china-invades-america-because-of-debt.html |title=The Long-Delayed Red Dawn Remake Could Have Been Scarily Topical |author=Brodesser-Akner, Claude |work=Vulture |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-01-05 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303061959/https://www.vulture.com/2011/12/red-dawn-china-invades-america-because-of-debt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。制片人特里普·文森（{{lang|en|Trip Vinson}}）表示：“我们最初非常不愿意作任何改变，但经过慎重考虑，我们构建了制作一部更加可怕、更具有智慧且更有威胁感的《赤色黎明》的办法，我们相信这提升了电影的水准<ref name="LA Times">{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-china-red-dawn-20110316,0,995726.story |title=Reel China: Hollywood tries to stay on China's good side |author1=Fritz, Ben |author2=Horn, John |lastauthoramp=yes |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-03-16 |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2012-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509171310/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-china-red-dawn-20110316,0,995726.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

