[[File:Q&A_Red_Dawn_world_premiere.jpg|thumb]]、[[乔希·佩克|乔希·佩克]]、特里普·文森（{{lang|en|Tripp Vinson}}）与[[奇幻电影节|奇幻电影节]]创办人蒂姆·里格（{{lang|en|Tim League}}）在影片于[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]的全球首映礼上。]]
2011年9月，据报道[[米高梅|米高梅]]正在与独立工作室{{le|FilmDistrict|FilmDistrict}}完成电影美国发行权的交易<ref name="LA Times2">{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/09/red-dawn-remake-to-come-out-next-year-from-filmdistrict.html |title='Red Dawn' remake to come out next year from FilmDistrict |author1=Fritz, Ben |author2=Horn, John |lastauthoramp=yes |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-09-26 |accessdate=2011-09-27 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206095127/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/09/red-dawn-remake-to-come-out-next-year-from-filmdistrict.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年12月，FilmDistict透过[[开路电影|开路电影]]达成将电影包含在其2012年发行片单中的协议<ref>{{cite news |last=Frankel |first=Daniel |date=2011-12-06 |title=FilmDistrict has reached deals to distribute its 2012 titles through Open Road |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/06/idUS99826269220111206 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2011-12-14 |archive-date=2012-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417155049/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/06/idUS99826269220111206 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年9月，据宣布影片将于2012年9月27日在[[奇幻电影节|奇幻电影节]]闭幕当日，在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]{{le|阿拉莫库房电影院|Alamo Drafthouse Cinema}}首映<ref>{{cite news |last=Clark |first=Noelene |date=2012-09-02 |title=‘Red Dawn’: Controversial remake to debut at Fantastic Fest in Austin |url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2012/09/05/red-dawn-controversial-remake-to-debut-at-fantastic-fest-in-austin/ |publisher=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2012-09-05 |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116040808/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2012/09/05/red-dawn-controversial-remake-to-debut-at-fantastic-fest-in-austin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片于2012年11月21日在美国影院上映。

=== 票房 ===
影片首映首两日收益740万美元，首周末凭借1460万美元位居票房榜第七位<ref>{{cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=November 23, 2012 |title='Twilight,' 'Skyfall' Devour Newcomers on Turkey Day |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3573&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDB |accessdate=2012-11-26 |archive-date=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814232546/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3573&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=2012-11-25 |title=Weekend Report: 'Twilight,' Bond Dominate Fruitful Thanksgiving |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3574&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDB |accessdate=2012-11-26 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007004540/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3574&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片于2013年2月21日在影院下线，全球总票房约4817万美元<ref name="Mojo" /><ref name="Boxoffice.com" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
影片受到影评人的强烈批评。{{le|评论聚合网站|Review aggregator}}[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据131条评论给影片打出12%的新鲜度，平均得分3.8分（满分10）。网站共识指出：“重制的《赤色黎明》缺乏原版的时事性，但向对角色发展和总体逻辑传递做出的不够重视至少是一次致敬<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/red_dawn_2012/ |title=Red Dawn (2012) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2012-11-20 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226103956/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/red_dawn_2012 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据33条评论给影片打出31分（满分100），表示“非常差”。影片获得[[金酸梅奖|金酸梅奖]]最差前传、重制、恶搞及续集电影提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.razzies.com/history/13winners.asp|title=The 33rd Annual RAZZIE® Awards|accessdate=2013-07-11|work=Razzies.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130227010807/http://www.razzies.com/history/13winners.asp|archivedate=2013-02-27}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的{{le|弗兰克·舍克|Frank Scheck}}表示：“这部不明智的1984年[[约翰·米利厄斯|约翰·米利厄斯]]热门动作片重拍版笨手笨脚地对待了已经傻透了了的前车之鉴<ref>{{cite news |last=Scheck |first=Frank |date=2012-11-15 |title=Red Dawn: Film Review |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/red-dawn-hemsworth-hutcherson-389791 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2012-11-19 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121119073015/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/red-dawn-hemsworth-hutcherson-389791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的{{le|马诺拉·达吉斯|Manohla Dargis}}表示：“布拉德利......处理低成本动作片很棒，这有利于从廉价的特效、糟糕的演技和政治题材中转移注意力<ref>{{cite news |last=Dargis |first=Manohla |date=November 20, 2012 |title=He’s Lost the Game. Can He Beat the Koreans? |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2012/11/21/movies/red-dawn-remake-trades-soviets-for-north-koreans.html |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2012-11-21 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530120153/http://movies.nytimes.com/2012/11/21/movies/red-dawn-remake-trades-soviets-for-north-koreans.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的马克·奥尔森（{{lang|en|Mark Olsen}}）认为，“合乎情理地迷迷糊糊地沉醉了自身，重拍版《赤色黎明》就像踩中地雷一样根本无法在现实问题中站稳脚跟<ref>{{cite news |last=Olsen |first=Mark |date=November 20, 2012 |title=Review: 'Red Dawn' remake won't win hearts and minds |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-red-dawn-20121121,0,1603905.story |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2012-11-21 |archive-date=2013-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330120740/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-red-dawn-20121121,0,1603905.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]表示，“剧情的时间框架很容易混淆模糊。朝鲜花了多长时间才登陆并开始执行计划？他们的游戏计划是什么？这是一次国家入侵吗？我们还不知道美国其他地方发生了什么事<ref>{{cite news |last=Ebert |first=Roger |date=November 20, 2012 |title=Red Dawn |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20121120/REVIEWS/121129997 |work=Chicago Sun-Times |accessdate=2012-11-21 |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116151235/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20121120%2FREVIEWS%2F121129997 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

相反，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的乔·雷伊顿（{{lang|en|Joe Leydon}}）给予影片积极评价，写道：“战争场面充满了推动性的紧迫感，因此布拉德利（一位认真的动作指导和第二单元导演）往往给影片一种半纪录片的影子”<ref>{{cite news |last=Leydon |first=Joe |date=2012-09-27 |title=Red Dawn |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117948435/ |work=Variety |accessdate=2012-11-19 |archive-date=2013-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105091521/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117948435/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

